import React from 'react';
import {
  Box,
  Typography,
  Button,
  Chip,
  Paper,
  TextField,
  Link,
} from '@mui/material';
import { styled } from '@mui/material/styles';

const categories = [
  'Business',
  'Marketing',
  'Research',
  'News',
  'Sales',
  'Devops',
  'Other',
];

const TaskCard = styled(Paper)(({ theme }) => ({
  padding: theme.spacing(2),
  marginBottom: theme.spacing(2),
  borderRadius: '12px',
  display: 'flex',
  alignItems: 'center',
  gap: theme.spacing(2),
}));

const CategoryChip = styled(Chip)(({ theme, selected }) => ({
  borderRadius: '16px',
  padding: '4px 8px',
  backgroundColor: selected ? theme.palette.primary.main : 'transparent',
  color: selected ? theme.palette.common.white : theme.palette.text.primary,
  '&:hover': {
    backgroundColor: selected ? theme.palette.primary.dark : theme.palette.action.hover,
  },
}));

const Dashboard = () => {
  const [selectedCategory, setSelectedCategory] = React.useState('Business');

  return (
    <Box>
      <Box sx={{ mb: 4 }}>
        <Typography variant="h1" sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
          Greetings, Sanket
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary">
          What online tasks or research would you like Proxy to do for you?
        </Typography>
      </Box>

      <Box sx={{ 
        display: 'flex',
        gap: 1,
        flexWrap: 'wrap',
        mb: 4,
      }}>
        {categories.map((category) => (
          <CategoryChip
            key={category}
            label={category}
            selected={category === selectedCategory}
            onClick={() => setSelectedCategory(category)}
          />
        ))}
      </Box>

      <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', gap: 2, mb: 4 }}>
        <TaskCard sx={{ flex: 1 }}>
          <Box sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
            <Typography variant="h6">Company Sentiment Analysis</Typography>
            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', gap: 1, mt: 1 }}>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                Convergence
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                503
              </Typography>
              <Chip
                label="Business"
                size="small"
                sx={{ backgroundColor: 'primary.light', color: 'primary.main' }}
              />
            </Box>
          </Box>
        </TaskCard>

        <TaskCard sx={{ flex: 1 }}>
          <Box sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
            <Typography variant="h6">Review my Shopify store</Typography>
            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', gap: 1, mt: 1 }}>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                Convergence
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                355
              </Typography>
              <Chip
                label="Business"
                size="small"
                sx={{ backgroundColor: 'primary.light', color: 'primary.main' }}
              />
            </Box>
          </Box>
        </TaskCard>
      </Box>

      <Box sx={{ textAlign: 'center', color: 'text.secondary', mt: 4 }}>
        <Typography variant="body2">
          By messaging Proxy, you agree to our{' '}
          <Link href="#" color="primary">
            Terms
          </Link>
          {' '}and{' '}
          <Link href="#" color="primary">
            AI Policy
          </Link>
        </Typography>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Dashboard;
